  <section class="bento" id="features">
    <div class="bento-inner">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <div class="tag">Features</div>
        <h2>Built for speed and privacy.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-grid reveal-stagger">
        <div class="card bento-card wide"><div class="card-icon">🔍</div><h3>Convert All Code to Diagrams</h3><p>Scans your entire document for Mermaid code blocks and renders them all as high-quality images in one click. No manual work.</p></div>
        <div class="card bento-card"><div class="card-icon">✏️</div><h3>Insert Mermaid Diagram</h3><p>Side-by-side editor with instant preview, syntax highlighting, and templates.</p></div>
        <div class="card bento-card"><div class="card-icon">🔄</div><h3>Edit Selected Mermaid Image</h3><p>Click any diagram image and edit its source in place — no copy-paste needed.</p></div>
        <div class="card bento-card wide"><div class="card-icon">🩹</div><h3>Fix Copied Markdown</h3><p>Google Docs mangles Mermaid syntax when you copy from markdown. This tool repairs vertical tabs, stray backticks, and broken formatting so your diagrams render correctly. <a href="/features" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline">Learn more →</a></p></div>
        <div class="card bento-card"><div class="card-icon">🖼️</div><h3>Convert Image to Code</h3><p>Extract the original Mermaid source from any diagram image inserted by this add-on.</p></div>
        <div class="card bento-card"><div class="card-icon">📋</div><h3>Templates &amp; Gallery</h3><p>Jump-start with flowcharts, sequences, ER diagrams, and 14 more types. <a href="/gallery" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline">Browse gallery →</a></p></div>
        <div class="card bento-card wide"><div class="card-icon">🔒</div><h3>Zero Data Collection</h3><p>No analytics. No cookies. No telemetry. No servers. Your documents never leave your browser — rendering is 100% client-side via mermaid.js. The only external request is loading the mermaid.js library from <a href="https://www.jsdelivr.com/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline">jsDelivr</a>.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
